gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.main

Class MudrodEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.main.MudrodEngine

  • public class MudrodEngine
extends Object
    Main entry point for Running the Mudrod system. Invocation of this class is tightly linked to the primary Mudrod configuration which can be located at config.xml.
